5:
Look, look! Isn't this outfit adorrrable?
Do mew love it? Do mew LOVE IT?!
9: Pipe down, yeesh... It's just clothes.
13:
*Gasp* Mew can't pull the catnip
over my eyes! Mew DO love it!
22:
Well, I think it suits you. Really
complements your ears and tail!
27:
Fur real?! Mew-mew knew she was a
fashion genius—Mew-Mew can
wear anything!
32:
It is very lovely. Is that a style from
Yamato?
35:
Bingo! I heard all the kits and cats
over there wear these traditional
get-ups for the new year!
37:
Ooh, I can't want to show off this
purrfect ensemble! You kits are
ready to go, right?
41:
Raaawr! Hurry it up, people! I'll leave
you behind!
45:
Wait, are you... Aaaaah! Yes, you ARE
Mew! You're so cute—I can't believe
I've bumped into you!
48:
Mweh-heh-heh! Lucky fella! Keep
the praise a-comin'!
52: She's really letting it get to her head.
56:
The new year is upon us. There is no
better time to give ourselves over to
revelry.
59:
Finally, I've found you! You are Mew,
aren't you?!
64:
Oh, thank the skies above! I know
this is sudden, but would you please
perform at Pal Fest 5?
68: Pal Fest 5? Mew mean THE Pal Fest 5?
75:
Only the hippest summer festival to
grace Palpebra District 5!
79:
Ah, so it's a local shindig! Wait, then
how'd you know about it, Mew?!
82:
We've heard how you drive crowds
of fans wild! If you perform at our
event, we'll be the best festival ever!
85:
MYAAACK?! Mew want Mew-Mew on
stage?! But, but she needs time to
prepare!
89:
I'm sure they'll love you out there. I
mean, have you been LISTENING to
this guy?
93:
Myaaah... What do I do? Mew-Mew's
never been on stage before. What if
it turns to kitty litter?
98: I'm sure you'll be all right, Mew.
102:
Well, if mew believe in Mew-Mew,
then maybe...
107:
Argh, hurry up and make a decision.
Time's a-wastin'.
111:
Mreowr! If mew guys insist so much,
Mew-mew has no choice but to
perform!
119:
MYAAAACK! Th-there's so many
people watching!
123:
*Gulp* Mew-Mew's nerves are shot
and her tumbly's all rumbly... Eep,
hope that's a hairball coming up...
126:
Our next act has the cutest ears and
tail in all the land! Please give a big
hand for the singing, dancing
wondercat...
128:
Mew in the MEEEWsical spectacular,
Kitty Conga!
131:
Singing, dancing?! Mew-Mew never
promised that!
141:
Whoa! Did you see how high she
leapt?!
143:
Yeah! She went ears over tail! So
freaking cute!
145:
I think she was looking right at me...
I'm gonna faint...
156:
Myeowzers... The festival people
specifically scouted Mew-Mew for
this event, but she blew-blew it.
157:
Mew-Mew was so excited, with her
fancy clothes... She shoulda just
sang instead of turning tail...
162:
Mya-la-laaaa... 
You're the yarn of my life, I'll chase
you to the end of my days!
Meow-ow-ow!
166:
Well, well, if you aren't a regular
chanteuse.
171: MYAAAH! When did mew get there?!
176:
I would love to hear you sing some
more, Mew.
189:
Then Mew-Mew super regrrrets
flying off the stage! Grrr, can we do
a take back?!
193:
Wait! Now that Mew-Mew is genius
singer, does this mean she's
reached her final form?!
198:
Only thing final here is my stress
level...
202:
Mew can't expect Mew-Mew to relax
after learning she's a born idol!
209:
So, Mew, in Yamato they have a
tradition of declaring a new year's
resolution...
213:
Do they? Then Mew-Mew declares
she will learn to stand in front of
people without losing her marbles!
215:
And then, after conquering her fears,
she'll be the cutest, hottest, wildest,
cattiest dancer everrr!
219: That's a lot for one resolution...
223:
Watch out! Mew-Mew's gonna
spend this year training, so she can
take next year by storm!
